title: South Park Complete Season 1-16 420p 720p TinyMP4
description:
South Park Season 1-16 - TinyMP4

An attempt to bring great quality with smaller file sizes!

Video: MPEG4 x264
Audio: MPEG4 FAAC

Season 1-4 + Extras SD
Resolution: 640x480
Filtered/Upscaled DVD Rips.

Season 5-16 + Movie HD
Resolution: 1280x720
Combination BDRips and Web-DL.

Includes: Bigger Longer and Uncut, Jesus vs. Frosty, Jesus vs. Santa, and the Unaired Pilot version of "Cartman Gets an Anal Probe".

- Seasons 11 - 16 should be uncensored. Seasons before 11 were never uncensored.
- Episode "Super Best Friends" is SD quality. No 720p version was ever made.
- Season 10 is kinda whiteish. You can use VLC player with filters (+contrast).
- Files are about as small as they can be without a huge quality loss (+/- 5-10%).
- Sizes vary: videos are encoded at a constant quality and not a constant size.
- Some attempt was made to normalize the audio volume level across all episodes.
- If you want the absolute best definitive quality, this torrent is not for you.

If you prefer the episodes in "Season" folders, rename file "CreateFolders.txt" to "CreateFolders.bat". Copy to directory with episodes and run it. TPB would not allow batch files in the video category so I had to upload as a text file. Before doing this please make sure to seed for awhile!
